oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Young boy fishing from boat dock with dog in Harrison Bay State Park, Tenn.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of a young boy fishing with a small dog from a boat dock in the Harrison Bay State Park. The boy is using crickets as bait and has a small fish on his fishing rod. The boy is wearing shorts. In the background there is various sizes of boats and houseboats as well as a large building .
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
